data.description: Ready for immediate move in. The Excite home lives up to its expectations. A quality built home that will provide the perfect living space for your family. This 3 bedroom, 2 bath home offers an open floor plan concept that features 17x 17 ceramic tile that flows as far as your eye can see as you walk through the front door. All living areas include tile floors so you don't have to upgrade with carpet in the bedrooms only. This home comes with 9'4" ceilings letting in the natural light and opens up your living spaces. The kitchen features ample cabinetry with grey - 42" upper cabinets for extra storage, a spacious island with sink, granite countertops and Samsung stainless steel appliances including a glass top range, microwave over the range, dishwasher and 25cf side by side refrigerator. Also included is a brick paver driveway, washer/dryer, blinds on all windows, 16 SEER a/c and our SMART home technology package. Situated on an oversized homesite with a large backyard, a 6ft vinyl fence is included across the rear of the property. This home provides outstanding, unique features that separate Park Square Homes from any other homebuilder.  Tarpon Bay is a brand new community in Haines City with future pool and cabana, sports park and dog park that will one day be home to over 350 families. Enjoy the Excite-ment of owning your dream home today.
